1 NOTE BERNETTE N. "BUNNY" CENTER, 87, died Tuesday, April 29, 2008, in Atlanta.

Graveside services were held May 1 at Crest Lawn Memorial Park with Rabbi Neil Sandler officiating.

Mrs. Center was born Jul
2 CONC y 2, 1920, in Atlanta. She was a full-time homemaker.

She was the widow of Dave Center.

Survivors include daughters and son-in-law Charlene Berman of Chappaqua, N.Y., and Renie and Fred Halperin of 
2 CONC Atlanta; son and daughter-in-law Charles and Jane Center of Atlanta; sister and brother-in-law Charlotte and Harry Gordon of Atlanta; eight grandchildren; and 10 great-grandchildren with another on th
2 CONC e way.

Her family expresses gratitude to her companion and friend Nicole Cullars.
