1 NOTE <p>From http://www.loebtree.com/maharal.html#sinai</p><p><p></p></p><p>Bezalel ben Ha├»m LOEB (LOEW) was born about 1480. Unlike his young brothre, stayed behind to help his father and did not pursue 
2 CONC studies in Poland. Bezalel married the daughter of Rabbi Chaim ISSEMHEIMER or married daughter of Rabbi Yitzchak KLOBER of Worms. (See discussion on p. 35 of The ESKELES Genealogy by Zeev ESHKOLOT.)
