2 CONC s: GEORGE BRIGHT/BRECHT, MICHAEL BRIGHT/BRECHT, CATHERINA (or KATHERINE) SHEETS (born Bright/Brecht), John Bright/Brecht, Peter Brecht/Bright, Maria WHITTENMEYER (born Bright/Brecht), Sarah Jones (bor
2 CONC n Bright/Brecht), Christina Pechin (born BRECHT/BRIGHT) and David Brecht/Bright.
