George Bright, s/o John and Margaret (Schaeffer) Brecht, was married to Eve Elizabeth (Stover) Bright with whom he had 8 children, Davi
2 CONC d, Sophia, Margaret, Catharine, John, George, Michael and Samuel Bright.
George Bright was a War of 1812 Veteran with Navy per Military Records and Department of Veterans Affairs Centre County PA.

