Margaret Hunt was born about 1721 in Pennsylvania.

Margaret Hunt married John Beals on 13 November 1738 in Pennsylvania. On
2 CONC  the 27th day, 5th month, 1758 (27 May 1758), at New Garden Monthly Meeting in Rowan County (now Guilford), North Carolina, Margaret and John were received on certificate from Hopewell Monthly Meeting
2 CONC , Frederick County, Virginia. It is probable that their children came with them.

Margaret died on 11 April 1796 in Guilford County, North Carolina.

Children of Margaret Hunt and John Beals
* Ruth Be
2 CONC als b. a 1740
* Lydia Beals b. a 1742
* Hannah Beals b. a 1745, d. 4 Feb 1804

