(Sir) William Griffith and Jane Stradling and their 13 children.  

http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:eXfSOpZ8MEUJ:www.themor
2 CONC risclan.com/GENEALOGY/GRIFFITH%2520William%2520F61348.html+pedigree,+dorothy+griffith+born+anglesay,born+wales1507&hl=nl&gl=be&strip=1

