2 CONC ollection and is based on the same set of yearbooks. Thanks to this name index users will enjoy improved name searching and more relevant <a id="" href="http://www.myheritage.com/help-center#/path/951
2 CONC 695781" class="green">Record Matches</a> to their family members found in these books. In case you didnŌĆÖt find what you were looking for, we encourage you to check out the U.S Yearbooks 1890-1979 co
2 CONC llection to search the entire free-text index of this amazing collection.
